h1. nullable

h2. Purpose

Allows a property to be set to @null@. By default Griffon does not allow @null@ values for properties.

h2. Examples

{code:java}
age nullable: true
{code}

h2. Description

Set to @true@ if the property allows @null@ values.

This constraint influences [schema generation|guide:grormConstraints].

Error Code: @className.propertyName.nullable@

{note}
Set the [blank|constraints] constraint to @false@ to ensure that an empty value fails validation.
{note}
